b1733f03c6589353169935d37bb633f4","tid":1525691,"uid":139173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T02:22:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aDVS9f3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaDVS9f3.jpg&h=bb9f6031&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"43aa64cf8a66c9c19f1691b582761c13474f5c34","tid":1525691,"uid":2920,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T02:22:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bTDUDaA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbTDUDaA.png&h=8f51a702&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3cdd1021855b6b906e652d78aa9339d7df3d271a","tid":1525691,"uid":2920,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T02:23:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oqwfnCo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoqwfnCo.jpg&h=21dca710&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"55c8259fe170ff71fa39343a9a7378cf1c1d9867","tid":1525691,"uid":94978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T02:28:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e22142a662efdc67053f8835031a99f4aeff123a","tid":1525691,"uid":2920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T02:29:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8592e532a67a991e6873f8d17ee093ab66bf2f73","tid":1525691,"uid":241536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T02:29:35.000Z","msg":"b"},{"pid":"dd509308b3bdc95ee956f6f559660b3ecc251998","tid":1525691,"uid":241536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T02:32:10.000Z","msg":"b"},{"pid":"3d5a51a86fca874a24fca5aaeef54603ff92bbb3","tid":1525691,"uid":143699,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T02:34:23.000Z","msg":"大家冇需要再俾錢搭黨鐵啦，直接跳啦。大家唔好有任何嘅心理壓力，721，呢個月嘅封站，再加上今晚黨鐵嘅處理手法。佢唔再值得香港人俾一分一毫，我地一於全民跳閘<br />\n<br />\n1.呢隻係最簡單嘅跳法，肥啲都跳到，手腳並用，真係冇難度架，跳多兩次就會熟手。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Aimi1zO.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAimi1zO.gif&h=e6d946f6&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n2.呢隻係新閘機，跳嘅時侯部機會響，要快手啲。同埋佢閘之間嘅距離有啲遠。用第一種跳法可能冇咁就手，建議直接跳過去，可以加個小助跑，都唔會太難。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iETUzUQ.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiETUzUQ.gif&h=c8f39564&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n3. 呢種方法會比較安全。因為直接跳閘點都會有cctv影到，但係跳欄杆嘅話可以搵啲盲位／暗位，難啲發現。不過跳嘅難度會比較高。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tRMSmzS.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtRMSmzS.gif&h=73d4b461&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">同場加映錯誤示範</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MBkjO1B.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMBkjO1B.gif&h=c106dd4c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢位狗狗好明顯冇睇教學片啦，大家千奇唔好學佢啊，動作要標準。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n注意事項：<br />\n－最好帶返口罩，遮一遮，保障返自已<br />\n－唔洗驚俾人捉到，就算俾人發現咗都可以直接跑走唔理佢，佢唔會真係追你9條街，當你離開咗佢個站嘅範圍，佢冇權捉你<br />\n－入閘時睇清楚有冇黃衫或可疑人士。真係得自已一個可以直接用第三招跳，最難捉。<br />\n－出閘嘅時侯更加唔洗驚，跳完係最近嘅出口快快手走人就得，唔會捉到你。<br />\n－其實仲有個安全啲嘅出閘方法，出閘果陣去客務到同佢講話岩岩係邊個邊個站嚟，但係跌咗張飛，問佢點算。你扮下野佢多數會俾一張一次性嘅綠色出閘卡你。我試過用呢招幾次都成功。<br />\n－黃衫人都係打份工，唔會同你咁搏命，都係果句，俾人捉到，大膽啲跑走唔好理佢<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">屌你老母狗鐵，你唔配收香港人錢呀。一齊跳佢老母閪！</span></span><br />\n完整示範片段：<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/pLjuuYOyhk8?list=LLDdGX5puzbpkSMVfjKqEnEA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FpLjuuYOyhk8%3Flist%3DLLDdGX5puzbpkSMVfjKqEnEA&d=LDhKEJhCApGKQi337qR8bxPX6nNrjY8iteK6A9FjwF0%3D&h=cfe74b46\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/pLjuuYOyhk8?list=LLDdGX5puzbpkSMVfjKqEnEA</a>"},{"pid":"f74e4b263e788bacc6cf374a7a1625f0e5aa2031","tid":1525691,"uid":2920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T03:09:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a0760d97ad9d4867debe40741289156561874bb6","tid":1525691,"uid":241536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T03:45:54.000Z","msg":"b"},{"pid":"6e1aa899f9ecde99e3c524c761f2b35769e7ac70","tid":1525691,"uid":2920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T03:52:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d39372002e884958d6c568bbe50c3a584e93cacd","tid":1525691,"uid":2920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T03:53:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/J7hqLkV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJ7hqLkV.jpg&h=6431e716&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3858af89a8db3ba7d063c032b6875754f08b778b","tid":1525691,"uid":259329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T03:54:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f2fa780b9838a28fcc2e5d8ae47eb6738ca66b2e","tid":1525691,"uid":175091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T03:55:37.000Z","msg":"起身冇晒機場po 推"},{"pid":"9d9ac4085334baeb2bc25e18addccb8db9a78d59","tid":1525691,"uid":241536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T03:57:55.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">有車就去機場shell入油，入油姐好nice<br />\n<br />\n冇車就排巴士，去影飛機<br />\n<br />\n無限loop<br />\n<br />\n1300見</span></span>"},{"pid":"d36c1a674da49faf8c31392955eed1ef23ed2bb6","tid":1525691,"uid":2662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T04:00:24.000Z","msg":"熱門要機場post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e87048efc7e38194d260b100f524484e0901b1d","tid":1525691,"uid":241536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T04:12:06.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">有車就去機場shell入油，入油姐好nice<br />\n<br />\n冇車就排巴士，去影飛機<br />\n<br />\n無限loop<br />\n<br />\n1300見</span></span>"}]}